title: NavigationHistoryEntry: key property
summary:
The key read-only property of the
  NavigationHistoryEntry interface returns the key of the history entry. This is a unique, UA-generated value that represents the history entry's slot in the entries list. It is used to navigate that particular slot via Navigation.traverseTo(). The key will be reused by other entries that replace the entry in the list (that is, if the NavigateEvent.navigationType is replace).
